v0.1.3

`collapse_bubble.py`
- Upgrade to `Truvari` v5.4.0 to fix an installation issue. Due to API changes in `Truvari`, this version of `collapse_bubble.py` must be used with `Truvari` v5.4.0 or later to generate identical results as previous versions.

v0.1.2

`collapse_bubble.py`
- Cluster bubbles by BFS to fix complex regions. Thanks to Quanyu Chen (@yeeus)
- Add more debug logging

v0.1.1

`collapse_bubble.py`
- Change default collapse parameters to `-r 500 -p 0.9 -P 0.9 -O 0`
- Slightly speed up

`merge_duplicates.py`
- Change the ID format of concatenated variants.